PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782483502
OL,3,CMayor accused of 'flip-flopping' over
OL,4,Ccontroversial Met Police tech contract
OL,6,FSir Sadiq Khan has been accused of
OL,7,F'flip-flopping' over controversial
OL,8,F#50m tech contract for the Met Police.
OL,10,FThe mayor initially blocked a deal
OL,11,Fafter he said the force only spoke to
OL,12,Fone supplier - tech giant Palantir.
OL,14,FHis intervention was subject to a
OL,15,Flegal challenge by the Florida-based
OL,16,Fcompany.
OL,18,FSir Sadiq has now given an extra 12
OL,19,Fmonths to run a pilot while the force
OL,20,Fsorts out a permanent long-term
OL,21,Fsupplier.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782483502
OL,3,CMayor accused of 'flip-flopping' over
OL,4,Ccontroversial Met Police tech contract
OL,6,F"We are pleased MOPAC has approved the
OL,7,FMet to continue to use this capability
OL,8,Ffor a further 12 months to strengthen
OL,9,Fprofessional standards, root out
OL,10,Fmisconduct and increase public
OL,11,Fconfidence," Assistant Commissioner
OL,12,FRachel Williams said.
OL,14,F"As part of our a New Met for London
OL,15,FPlan, we set out a series of
OL,16,Fcommitments to improve standards and
OL,17,Ftackle poor culture.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782483502
OL,3,CMayor accused of 'flip-flopping' over
OL,4,Ccontroversial Met Police tech contract
OL,6,F"The vast majority of Met officers and
OL,7,Fstaff serve London with dedication and
OL,8,Fintegrity, and they ` and the wider
OL,9,Fpublic - rightly expect robust action
OL,10,Fagainst the small minority who abuse
OL,11,Ftheir position or undermine public
OL,12,Ftrust.
OL,14,F"Our pilot work has allowed the Met
OL,15,Ffor the first time to bring together
OL,16,Fdata it already lawfully holds in one
OL,17,Fplace to identify potential standards,
OL,18,Fwelfare or cultural concerns.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782483502
OL,3,CMayor accused of 'flip-flopping' over
OL,4,Ccontroversial Met Police tech contract
OL,6,F"The pilot project earlier this year
OL,7,Ffocussed on identifying potential
OL,8,Fconduct issues and a significant
OL,9,Fnumber of matters are now being
OL,10,Fprogressed by our professional
OL,11,Fstandards team.
OL,13,F"We will continue to work with MOPAC
OL,14,Fover procurement of technology at pace
OL,15,Ffor the longer-term. This is to
OL,16,Fsupport both our work on raising
OL,17,Fstandards and our ambitions to use the
OL,18,Ftechnology to streamline
OL,19,Fadministrative processes, close budget
OL,20,Fgaps and free up officers to police
OL,21,Fthe streets of London."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782483502
OL,3,CMayor accused of 'flip-flopping' over
OL,4,Ccontroversial Met Police tech contract
OL,6,FPalantir's system would allow the Met
OL,7,Fto cut 500 jobs in response to a
OL,8,Fbudget shortfall of #100 million this
OL,9,Fyear and #125 million next year.
OL,11,FThe police budget for 2026/27 included
OL,12,Fplans to cut a total of 1,150 jobs in
OL,13,Fthe force, with the work of 500 of
OL,14,Fthose to be covered by AI tools used
OL,15,Fto reduce the time taken to draw up
OL,16,Fintelligence reports and analyse
OL,17,Fmobile phones.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782483502
OL,3,CMayor accused of 'flip-flopping' over
OL,4,Ccontroversial Met Police tech contract
OL,6,FCommissioner Sir Mark Rowley said in
OL,7,FMarch 2026, the number of Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice Service officers per 100,000
OL,9,Fpopulation was lower than at any point
OL,10,Fsince 1981.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Mayor of London
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Deputy Mayor has required
OL,14,Fthe Met to run a new procurement
OL,15,Fprocess, open to a wide range of
OL,16,Fpotential suppliers, to choose the
OL,17,Flong-term provider of this capability.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782483502
OL,3,CMayor accused of 'flip-flopping' over
OL,4,Ccontroversial Met Police tech contract
OL,6,F"Recognising the Met's current needs,
OL,7,Fthe Met may extend the current pilot
OL,8,Fto retain existing capability while
OL,9,Fthis procurement takes place."
OL,11,FThe Home Office granted funding for an
OL,12,Fadditional 100 officers, but Sir Mark
OL,13,Fis pushing for an extra 300.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782483502
OL,3,CMayor accused of 'flip-flopping' over
OL,4,Ccontroversial Met Police tech contract
OL,6,FConservative Assembly member Susan
OL,7,FHall said: "Finally - a Labour U-turn
OL,8,FI can welcome. No doubt the role that
OL,9,FI and my Conservative colleagues have
OL,10,Fbeen playing in scrutinising the Mayor
OL,11,Fand his useless Deputy will have
OL,12,Fcontributed in part to this, by
OL,13,Fexposing how untenable the position
OL,14,Fwas.
OL,16,F"But this flip-flopping has real
OL,17,Fconsequences for Londoners who will
OL,18,Flose out as a result of the millions
OL,19,Fsquandered on chopping and changing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782483502
OL,3,CMayor accused of 'flip-flopping' over
OL,4,Ccontroversial Met Police tech contract
OL,6,F"We cannot afford to lose even a
OL,7,Fsingle frontline officer and if this
OL,8,Ffiasco has cost the taxpayer even a
OL,9,Fpenny I shall be beyond livid with Sir
OL,10,FSadiq and his useless team."
